I implemented the LinUCB algorithm proposed by the paper from https://arxiv.org/pdf/1003.0146.pdf

There is only one hyper-paramter, namely, alpha. I grid-searched the value of alpha, and following are the grid search result (the first column is the alpha value and the second column is the average regret on the test set):

